	": The quality of this movie isn't really spectacular, with a fair few improvements being known and visible - and some of the RNG manipulating action sometimes feels a bit slow, although that might really just be a limitation of the game. That said, the potential improvements are not massive deal-breakers and the movie still holds itself up as good enough in technical quality overall.
	$LF
