	"On the subject of the category, it is mildly arbitrary, but it is clearly defined and does make a good showcase of what a TAS of 4th gen Pok√©mon looks like without glitching to the end and skipping the vast majority of the game as the any% movie does. For that reason, I think there is good enough merit to publish this TAS, and as such, accepting to Moons as a new category.
	$LF
